707213f-a.title: Brooklyn: Veronica Pl. - Cortelyou Rd.
707213f-a.text:
Veronica Place, north from Cortelyou Road. The small frame house
in the foreground, was razed between 1925 and 1928.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
